idn't%20employ%20smugglers%20but%20relied%20on%20customs%20officials%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20are%2C%20by%20their%20nature%2C%20very%20corrupt%2C%26quot%3B%20Malyuk%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20a%20certain%20stage%2C%20they%20actually%20played%20to%20our%20advantage%20in%20delivering%20the%20cabins%20I%20mentioned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299fe0f26-596b-4763-b90b-7765b6b5c520%5C%22%3EA%20fake%20company%20with%20drivers%20in%20the%20dark%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMalyuk%20said%20that%20Ukraine%2C%20through%20its%20agents%20in%20Russia%2C%20created%20a%20logistics%20company%20that%20purchased%20five%20vehicles%20and%20rented%20warehouse%20space%20for%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20warehouses%20was%20even%20in%20the%20same%20city%20block%20as%20Russia's%20Federal%20Security%20Service%20headquarters%20in%20the%20Chelyabinsk%20region%2C%20the%20security%20service%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalyuk%20added%20that%20the%20shell%20logistics%20company%20hired%20Russian%20citizens%20as%20truck%20drivers%2C%20sending%20them%20on%20multiple%20regular%20delivery%20jobs%20to%20avoid%20suspicion%20before%20springing%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blurry%20aerial%20image%20of%20a%20Tu-95%20%26quot%3BBear%26quot%3B%20bomber%20at%20an%20air%20base.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683df8196ffb6822ec61e8c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20struck%20aircraft%20like%20this%20Tu-95%20%26quot%3BBear%26quot%3B%20bomber%20at%20air%20bases%20across%20Russia%20on%20June%201.%3Cp%3EEYEPRESS%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20service%20chief%20said%20these%20drivers%20were%20only%20told%20to%20deliver%20the%20cabins%20near%20the%20airbases%2C%20whereupon%20a%20customer%20was%20meant%20to%20arrive%20and%20pay%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drivers%20themselves%20were%20left%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20Malyuk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20chief%20said%20that%20when%20one%20of%20the%20drivers%20inadvertently%20saw%20the%20drones%20inside%20one%20cabin%2C%20Ukrainian%20agents%20told%20him%20the%20systems%20were%20hunting%20tools%20for%20observing%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20they%20committed%20no%20illegal%20acts%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20intent%20in%20their%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20Malyuk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SBU%20chief%20also%20said%20that%20his%20team%20wanted%20to%20launch%20the%20attack%20in%20May%20but%20hit%20several%20delays%2C%20including%20the%20drivers%20getting%20drunk%20during%20the%20Easter%20holiday%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Malyuk%2C%20each%20truck-mounted%20cabin%20included%20solar%20panels%20and%20a%20battery%20to%20keep%20the%20drones%20charged%20and%20ready%20for%20deployment%20in%20cold%20weather%3B%20the%20quadcopters%20were%20launched%20in%20temperatures%20as%20low%20as%20104%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20created%20additional%20difficulties%20in%20bringing%20these%20cabins%20into%20the%20territory%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%2C%20because%20these%20types%20of%20goods%20simply%20can't%20be%20taken%20there%2C%20since%20Russia%20is%20under%20sanctions%2C%26quot%3B%20Malyuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20service%20chief%20declined%20to%20share%20further%20details%20about%20the%20smuggling%20process%2C%20but%20said%20his%20team%20went%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20seven%20circles%20of%20hell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20designed%20attack%20drones%20specifically%20for%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Spiderweb%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20each%20could%20carry%20a%20payload%20of%201.6%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20hit%20about%20a%20third%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi