%26quot%3B'no%20shoes'%20startup%20offices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20startup%20leaders%20started%20to%20chime%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20no%20shoes%20and%20no%20pants%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Kyle%20Sherman%2C%20founder%20of%20Flowhub%2C%20a%20cannabis%20software%20company%20based%20in%20Denver%2C%20commented.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BShorts%20are%20required%20though.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESherman%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20this%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Hsu%2C%20cofounder%20of%20SF-based%20Speak%2C%20a%20language%20learning%20app%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Speak%20confirmed%20the%20no-shoes%20policy%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bemployees%20get%20a%20slipper%20stipend%20when%20they%20join%20the%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpeak's%20first%20market%20in%202019%20was%20South%20Korea%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Speak%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20'policy'%20pays%20homage%20to%20the%20traditional%20Asian%20culture%20of%20no%20shoes%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20X%20users%20found%20the%20policy%20off-putting%2C%20mainly%20fretting%20about%20potential%20odor%20issues.%20Others%20found%20it%20to%20be%20an%20attractive%20job%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELang%20assured%20skeptical%20minds%20that%20%26quot%3Bshoe%20covers%2Fsplippers%26quot%3B%20are%20available%20at%20the%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20CEO%20Michael%20Truell%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20startup%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20working%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-shoeless-barefoot-offices-trend-photos-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno-shoes%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20a%20new%20trend%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Business%20Insider%20wrote%20in%