burned%20through%20almost%2011%20billion%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETokens%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20how%20AI%20models%20break%20queries%20down%20into%20digestible%20data%20chunks.%20Industry%20pricing%20is%20based%20on%20how%20many%20tokens%20are%20processed.%20That%20top-ranked%20developer's%20token%20usage%20costs%20almost%20%2435%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20this%20leaderboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20compares%20to%20the%20%24200%20a%20month%20he's%20been%20charged.%20Even%20if%20that's%20over%20a%20whole%20year%2C%20Anthropic%20would%20be%20getting%20about%20%242%2C400%2C%20while%20incurring%20much%20higher%20inference%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a675f0b1-797f-45f1-ab39-677872d24c56%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20is%20changing%20its%20pricing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20clearly%20unsustainable%2C%20so%20Anthropic%20plans%20to%20change%20its%20pricing.%20The%20%24200%20a%20month%20plan%20will%20stay%2C%20but%20the%20startup%20will%20introduce%20weekly%20rate%20limits%2C%20starting%20August%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20users%20blow%20through%20these%20new%20weekly%20rate%20limits%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20buy%20additional%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20identified%20extreme%20usage%20by%20a%20small%20number%20of%20customers%20that%20impacts%20capacity%20for%20our%20broader%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Anthropic%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20said%20it's%20also%20seen%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20violations%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20account%20sharing%20and%20reselling%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20committed%20to%20supporting%20advanced%20use%20cases%20long-term%2C%20but%20need%20to%20ensure%20consistent%20performance%20for%20all%20developers%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Anthropic%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22004cd51c-ef99-41a6-b90a-c755fac48afd%5C%22%3EA%20Swedish%20whale%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tracked%20down%20one%20of%20the%20whales%20near%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Claude%20Code%20Leaderboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlbert%20%C3%96rwall%2C%20a%20developer%20based%20in%20Sweden%2C%20said%20he's%20been%20using%20the%20%24200%20a%20month%20Claude%20Code%20subscription%20to%20build%20his%20own%20vibe-coding%20platform%2C%20along%20with%20some%20open-source%20agentic%20tools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20probably%20running%203%20to%204%20fairly%20long-running%20tasks%20in%20parallel%20constantly%20while%20I%20was%20working%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20it%20really%20took%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20his%20Claude%20Code%20usage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20excluding%20these%20big%20projects%2C%C2%A0%C3%96rwall%20said%20his%20regular%20workflow%20in%20Claude%20Code%20likely%C2%A0racks%20up%20inference%20costs%20of%20%24500%20per%20day%2C%20under%20a%20subscription%20that%20costs%20only%20%24200%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I'm%20guessing%20my%20workflow%20might%20not%20be%20sustainable%20for%20Anthropic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22666f72f6-c461-45e7-bda4-e007262d27d5%5C%22%3ECursor%20responded%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Anthropic's%20new%20pricing%20kicks%20in%2C%C2%A0%C3%96rwall%20said%20he'll%20keep%20the%20%24200%20a%20month%20subscription%20for%20a%20while%20to%20get%C2%A0a%20feel%20for%20what%20the%20weekly%20limits%20actually%20mean%20for%20his%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20avoid%20paying%20anything%20beyond%20the%20%24200%20subscription%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20can%20change%20how%20he%20writes%20code%20and%20develops%C2%A0projects%20to%20avoid%20breaching%20the%20new%20rate%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20I%20originally%20switched%20from%20Cursor%20to%20Claude%20Code%20was%20because%20usage-based%20pricing%20became%20too%20expensive%20in%20Cursor%2C%26quot%3B%20%C3%96rwall%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20is%20another%20popular%20AI%20coding%20service%2C%20which%20often%20uses%20Anthropic's%20AI%20models%20as%20the%20underlying%20intelligence%20powering%20its%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20recently%20switched%20its%20%2420%20a%20month%20Pro%20plan%20from%20unlimited%20requests%20to%20a%20tiered%20system%20with%20usage-based%20pricing%20for%20%26quot%3Bfast%26quot%3B%20requests%2C%20meaning%20users%20are%20charged%20extra%20for%20exceeding%20a%20certain%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20change%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20clear%20communication%2C%20caused%20confusion%20and%20frustration%20among%20some%20users%20who%20expected%20unlimited%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20announced%20the%20initial%20change%20in%20mid-June.%20Then%20it%20updated%20with%20more%20details%20about%202%20weeks%20later%2C%20and%20then%20again%20in%20early%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20models%20can%20spend%20more%20tokens%20per%20request%20on%20longer-horizon%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20startup%20wrote%20in%20a%20blog%20post%2C%20apologizing%20for%20surprising%20users%20with%20unexpected%20new%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20most%20users'%20costs%20have%20stayed%20fairly%20constant%2C%20the%20hardest%20requests%20cost%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%20more%20than%20simple%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22630f2f82-5d31-47f9-a5e9-e20d52ab3e60%5C%22%3EInference%20costs%20aren't%20falling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assumption%20across%20the%20industry%20has%20been%20that%20inference%20costs%20will%20drop%20dramatically%2C%20making%20these%20AI%20coding%20services%20more%20financially%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20this%20hasn't%20happened%20thus%20far.%20Instead%2C%20when%20a%20new%20top%20AI%20model%20comes%20out%2C%20all%20the%20AI%20coding%20services%20integrate%20it%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20its%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20faulty%20pillar%20of%20the%20'costs%20will%20drop'%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Ethan%20Ding%2C%20CEO%20of%20startup%20TextQL%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fethanding.substack.com%2Fp%2Fai-subscriptions-get-short-squeezed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%26quot%3BDemand%20exists%20for%20'the%20best%20language%20model%2C'%20period.%20And%20the%20best%20model%20always%20costs%20about%20the%20same%2C%20because%20that's%20what%20the%20edge%20of%20inference%20costs%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20and%20other%20AI%20users%20usually%20want%20the%20best%2C%20not%20last%20month's%20leading%20intelligence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20opens%20Claude%20and%20thinks%2C%20'you%20know%20what%3F%20let%20me%20use%20the%20shitty%20version%20to%20save%20my%20boss%20some%20money.'%20We're%20cognitively%20greedy%20creatures%2C%26quot%3B%20Ding%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20best%20brain%20we%20can%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20inference%20costs%20do%20fall%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20agentic%20AI%20workflows%20means%20that%20developers%20set%20up%20longer%2C%20automated%20projects%20that%20generate%20a%20lot%20more%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20project%20uses%20100%20million%20tokens%2C%20rather%20than%201%20million%2C%20the%20initiative's%20cost%20remains%20high%2C%20even%20if%20per-token%20prices%20may%20have%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20%2420%2Fmonth%20subscription%20cannot%20even%20support%20a%20user%20making%20a%20single%20%241%20deep%20research%20run%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Ding%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that's%20exactly%20what%20we're%20racing%20toward.%20Every%20improvement%20in%20model%20capability%20is%20an%20improvement%20in%20how%20much%20compute%20they%20can%20meaningfully%20consume.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%20to%20offer%20unlimited%20usage%20in%20this%20new%20world%20under%20any%20subscription%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20math%20has%20fundamentally%20broken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finference-whales-threaten-ai-coding-startups-business-model-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755017650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689a6fe7a17a8c5b4052acdc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finference-whales-threaten-ai-coding-startups-business-model-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20coding%20services%20face%20surging%20costs%20from%20heavy%20users%2C%20forcing%20startups%20such%20as%20Anthropic%20and%20Cursor%20to%20adjust%20pricing%20and%20even%20business%20models.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finference-whales-threaten-ai-coding-startups-business-model-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20is%20trying%20to%20poach%20Meta%20AI%20talent%20and%20offering%20multimillion-dollar%20pay%20packages%2C%20internal%20documents%20show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224411%