with%20the%20kite%2C%20Nadeem%20and%20Saud%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20years%20picking%20up%20other%20injured%20birds%20and%20placing%20them%20in%20safe%20places%20that%20will%20prevent%20them%20from%20being%20run%20over%20or%20choking%20in%20a%20gutter.%20But%20the%20fate%20of%20these%20birds%20would%20remain%20unknown.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20kept%20looking%20for%20help%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20siblings%20found%20another%20kite%20in%20a%20parking%20lot.%20This%20time%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20different%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20it%20to%20a%20veterinarian%20who%20had%20treated%20our%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20dog.%20He%20agreed%20to%20help%20us%2C%20and%20we%20were%20able%20to%20save%20the%20bird%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20then%20on%2C%20every%20injured%20bird%20they%20found%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20vet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20the%20number%20of%20birds%20increased%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20buy%20a%20cage.%20We%20released%20the%20birds%20on%20the%20rooftop%20during%20the%20day%20and%20put%20them%20in%20the%20cage%20after%20dark.%20Our%20neighbours%20appreciated%20our%20efforts%20and%20started%20pitching%20in%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20number%20of%20injured%20birds%20grew%20so%20high%20that%20they%20eventually%20converted%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275250%2Fdelhi-nest-man-builds-bird-bamboo-homes-trains-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroof%20into%20an%20enclosure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20rescued%20almost%20400%20birds%2C%20including%20owls%2C%20hawks%2C%20water%20hens%2C%20and%20egrets%20between%202003%20and%202010.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20an%20NGO%2C%20Wildlife%20Rescue%2C%20to%20take%20up%20the%20cause%2C%