20are%20minor.%20Otherwise%2C%20some%20birds%20sustain%20serious%20injuries.%20Some%20have%20gynaecological%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20eggs%20getting%20stuck%20while%20delivering.%20On%20other%20occasions%2C%20the%20chicks%20fall%20from%20the%20nest%20or%20juveniles%20get%20injured%20while%20learning%20how%20to%20fly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20bird%20species%20who%20come%20in%20for%20treatment%20also%20vary%20with%20season.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20kite%20bird%20season%20starts%20from%20March%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20at%20least%20500%20injured%20kites%20in%20the%20next%20two%20months.%20The%20number%20of%20rescued%20hawk%20birds%20will%20increase%20more%20during%20mid-summer.%20The%20highest%20number%20of%20birds%20are%20injured%20in%20August%2C%20as%20the%20number%20of%20people%20flying%20kites%20peaks%20during%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadeem%20says%20all%20the%20rescued%20birds%20are%20given%20balanced%20food%20with%20meat%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20treated%20by%20an%20expert%20veterinarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20birds%20recover%20and%20fly%2C%20while%20the%20birds%20with%20severe%20injuries%20feel%20highly%20stressed%20and%20die.%20Birds%20are%20psychologically%20vulnerable%2C%20and%20the%20trauma%20severely%20affects%20their%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProtecting%20the%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nadeem%20and%20Saud%E2%80%99s%20cause%20is%20noble%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20education%20in%20wildlife%20rescue.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20quit%20school%20in%201997%20as%20our%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20condition%20could%20not%20allow%20us%20to%20study%20further.%20Our%20parents%20wanted%20us%20to%20revive%20their%20business%2C%20so%20we%20started%20working%20at%20our%20bathroom%20fittings%20shop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-bl