xplains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20years%2C%20the%20brothers%20were%20using%20their%20own%20savings%20to%20fuel%20operations.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20donations%20from%20kind%20strangers%20have%20helped%20ease%20the%20financial%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaud%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20receiving%20donations%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20These%20partly%20support%20our%20cause.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20manage%20all%20the%20expenses%20from%20our%20earnings.%20We%20have%20also%20registered%20an%20NGO%2C%20Raptor%20Rescue%20and%20Research%20Inc%2C%20to%20raise%20funds%20in%20the%20US%20and%20help%20our%20cause%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%2040-year-old%20notes%20that%20the%20NGO%20needs%20more%20financial%20support.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20run%20on%20a%20limited%20budget.%20Many%20bird%20rescue%20calls%20coming%20from%20far%20corners%20of%20Delhi%20go%20unanswered.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20an%20ambulance%20and%20cannot%20travel%20far%20to%20rescue%20birds.%20Many%20people%20who%20wish%20to%20help%20us%20cannot%20bring%20them%20to%20our%20house%20for%20logistical%20reasons.%20Some%20fear%20handling%20birds%20of%20prey.%20Reaching%20out%20to%20birds%20from%20far-flung%20areas%20is%20difficult.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaud%20adds%20that%20receiving%20donations%20will%20help%20them%20cater%20to%20a%20farther%20geographic%20area.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20manage%20other%20daily%20issues%20and%20challenges%20at%20our%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20siblings%20plan%20to%20establish%20a%20full-fledged%20hospital%20for%20birds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20rented%20a%20small%20clinic%2C%20and%20more%20donations%20will%20help%20us%20build%20an%20adequate%20facility%20for%20the%20birds.%20Talks%20are%20also%20underway%20to%20receive%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20from%20the%20government%20for%20the%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-e